&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;At Engage Senior Therapy, we provide on-site physical therapy, occupational therapy, and speech therapy services to senior living communities across New England. Our team is committed to delivering compassionate, relationship-centered care that helps patients maintain mobility, independence, and confidence in their daily lives. Engage fosters strong clinical collaboration and a supportive environment where team members continue to grow while making a meaningful impact every day.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Our Clinical Affiliation Program&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Engage is honored to partner with the nation’s top PT, PTA, OT and SLP programs and provide aspiring clinicians with a unique, hands-on learning experience where you will learn, grow and make a difference in the lives of our patients. &lt;em&gt;*Must be currently enrolled and attending school for Physical Therapy/Physical Therapy Assistance, Occupational Therapy, or Speech Therapy)*&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Through our partnership with Fusion, we offer students two rotation options to complement the classroom setting:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outpatient: make an impact on a patient population of all ages. Work side-by-side with your Clinical Instructor (Ci), learning and treating a variety of conditions and diagnoses including arthritis, chronic pain, musculoskeletal, orthopedic, pre-post surgery, sports injuries, vestibular and balance, and women’s health.&amp;nbsp; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Senior Therapy: make an impact and provide access to care to a geriatric population living in Assisted Living and Memory Care locations. Work side-by- side with your CI, learning and treating a variety of conditions and offering programs for activities of daily living, fall prevention, functional mobility, movement disorders, orthopedic injuries, vestibular and balance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Throughout your time with us, we encourage you to ask questions, engage with patients, and immerse yourself in the practical aspects of your field. Your CI is eager to share their knowledge and expertise. Our goal is to provide you a transformative and enriching experience so that you leave understanding what great patient care is and feeling inspired and ready to make a positive impact, wherever you may practice next.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Engage invests in a culture of inclusion and positivity and encourage all to apply to our open roles. You will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, gender, gender identity or expression, sexual orientation, national origin, genetics, disability, age, or veteran status.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Engage is a proud member of &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fusionptpartners.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Fusion Physical Therapy Partners.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
